# timequota

Manage the time of your python script.

```python
from timequota import TimeQuota

tq = TimeQuota(2, "h")

# ...

tq.update()

for i in range(100):

    # ...

    will_exceed_time = tq.track()
    if will_exceed_time:
        # ...
        break
```


